title: Swamp Tomb of the Black One
story: For a long time the tomb of the Black One remained sealed. Lately a giant soul-sucking ape has made its home here.

notes.text: Some gold hidden in a crevice of the wall.
A lavishly decorated door with a keyhole to the south.
A broken strongbox with an uncanny, slightly translucent mace in it.
A bottomless well, turns a person to stone if a coin is dropped into it.
